pageContext.claim: “We're here today to celebrate a resounding victory for all of you, for northwest Ohio, and for our great military, and for our entire country. Incredible victory. After so many years of budget cuts and layoffs, today, jobs are coming back and pouring back, frankly, like never before.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump exaggerates job growth in Ohio since he's been president. It has continued to grow at about the same pace that started post-recession under the Obama administration.
